    "en": {
      "title": "A sudden meeting between Basil and Ranil",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Ranil Wickremesinghe and Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna national organizer and former minister Basil Rajapaksa are expected to meet today (18).",
        "A senior speaker of the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna said that the meeting will be held at the Presidential Secretariat.",
        "It is reported that the current situation in the country and plans to form a new government in the future will also be discussed.(R)"
      ],
